Package de.thm.mni.compilerbau.phases._04a_tablebuild

Class TableBuilder

java.lang.Object
de.thm.mni.compilerbau.absyn.visitor.DoNothingVisitor
de.thm.mni.compilerbau.phases._04a_tablebuild.TableBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visitor
public class TableBuilder extends DoNothingVisitor implements Visitor
This class is used to create and populate a SymbolTable containing entries for every symbol in the currently compiled SPL program. Every declaration of the SPL program needs its corresponding entry in the SymbolTable.

Calculated Types can be stored in and read from the dataType field of the Expression, TypeExpression or Variable classes.
